Articles.Content: Don't know. Should be. Give it a shot and let me know. Haven't even played 1.2 yet..

If anyone is interested let me know.
Latest commit on GitHub fixes a bug which wipes out all other IVA's. And fixes the Rafale's Normals not showing.
I cant live without this mod ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif ":D")
